RESPONSIBLE USE NOTICE

This software is provided for AUTHORIZED SECURITY TESTING and EDUCATIONAL
RESEARCH only. By using this software, you agree to:

1. Obtain proper written authorization before testing any systems
2. Comply with all applicable laws and regulations
3. Use this software only in controlled environments or with explicit permission
4. Maintain audit logs for compliance and incident reconstruction
5. Not use this software for malicious purposes

The framework explicitly EXCLUDES:
- Ransomware/wiper/destructive capabilities
- Supply chain attack tooling
- Automated mass exploitation

This project includes comprehensive detection documentation (YARA rules, Sigma
rules, IOCs) specifically to help defenders identify and respond to C2 activity.

Unauthorized access to computer systems is illegal. Users are solely responsible
for ensuring compliance with all applicable laws.
